{
  "texts": [
    "This heightened activity led to increased connectivity and coordination among the accounts within the disinformation network, thus resulting in the observed spike in efficiency.",
    "Our analysis sought to establish a correlation between the nature of network activity and its structure, emphasizing activities that could hint at coordinated behavior.",
    "For this reason, in this experiment we analyze the networks at different moments in time and correlate their content characteristics against their density and efficiency.",
    "First, in Fig. 7 we show the journalist and disinformation networks at different moments in time.",
    "Each dot in the graph is a node (Twitter account) of a given network, its size is proportional to the number of retweets it made during that period, and an edge exists if a retweet was made between those nodes."
  ]
}